00:47:31,390 --> 00:47:34,890
♪ Not much longer will you be mine ♪

935
00:47:34,935 --> 00:47:37,345
- [timid chuckle]

936
00:47:37,396 --> 00:47:39,186
[sighs]

937
00:47:39,231 --> 00:47:42,281
Glen. Glenda.

938
00:47:42,318 --> 00:47:46,738
It’s so nice to see your sweet faces.

